  <span id="freeText6991748176999667936" style="display:none">Very mad at myself that I waited this long to read this. I preferred her newest book (<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/54814834.Under_a_White_Sky_The_Nature_of_the_Future" title="Under a White Sky The Nature of the Future by Elizabeth Kolbert" rel="nofollow noopener">Under a White Sky: The Nature of the Future</a>), but this was still amazing.</span>
